TERMFOLIO(1)                                User Commands                                        TERMFOLIO(1)                                                     | !V1.0.0; !TW161/161; !NL72; 1:FC, BP2; 13:FP1, BP2; 130:FC; 142:FP1, BP2
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
NAME                                                                                                                                                              | 1:FC; 5:FP1, BP2
  termfolio - multilingual TUI for browsing ANSI text pages                                                                                                       | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
SYNOPSIS                                                                                                                                                          | 1:FC; 9:FP1, BP2
  termfolio --config PATH                                                                                                                                         | 3:Fg; 26:FP1, BP2
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
DESCRIPTION                                                                                                                                                       | 1:FC; 12:FP1, BP2
  termfolio renders ANSI content on multiple pages. Pages are defined by a YAML configuration file with                                                           | 
  languages and layers. Each layer maps a single key to a shell command that outputs ANSI text. The                                                               | 
  application then lets you switch layers and scroll long content from the terminal.                                                                              | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
CONFIGURATION                                                                                                                                                     | 1:FC; 14:FP1, BP2
  The YAML file defines languages and layers. Both are required.                                                                                                  | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
  langs:                                                                                                                                                          | 
    - code: language code (string, required)                                                                                                                      | 
      label: label shown in the footer                                                                                                                            | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
  layers:                                                                                                                                                         | 
    - key: single key used to switch to the layer                                                                                                                 | 
      label: per-language label shown in the footer                                                                                                               | 
      title: per-language title shown in the header                                                                                                               | 
      help: per-language help line shown under the menu                                                                                                           | 
      cmd: per-language shell command to produce ANSI output                                                                                                      | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
  Example:                                                                                                                                                        | 3:Fg; 11:FP1, BP2
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
  langs:                                                                                                                                                          | 3:Fg; 9:FP1, BP2
    - code: fr                                                                                                                                                    | 
      label: Fran√ßais                                                                                                                                             | 
    - code: en                                                                                                                                                    | 
      label: English                                                                                                                                              | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
  layers:                                                                                                                                                         | 1:Fg; 10:FP1, BP2
    - key: "D"                                                                                                                                                    | 
      label:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "Documentation"                                                                                                                                       | 
        en: "Documentation"                                                                                                                                       | 
      title:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "Documentation termfolio"                                                                                                                             | 
        en: "Termfolio Documentation"                                                                                                                             | 
      help:                                                                                                                                                       | 
        fr: "\x1b[90mHelp: \x1b[0m\x1b[33m> \x1b[0m\x1b[37mLiens cliquables\x1b[0m"                                                                               | 
        en: "\x1b[90mHelp: \x1b[0m\x1b[33m> \x1b[0m\x1b[37mClickable links\x1b[0m"                                                                                | 
      cmd:                                                                                                                                                        | 
        fr: "splitans -f neotex -F ansi docs/documentation-fr.neo"                                                                                                | 
        en: "splitans -f neotex -F ansi docs/documentation-en.neo"                                                                                                | 
    - key: "W"                                                                                                                                                    | 
      label:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "M√©t√©o"                                                                                                                                               | 
        en: "Weather"                                                                                                                                             | 
      title:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "M√©teo la plus proche"                                                                                                                                | 
        en: "Nearest weather"                                                                                                                                     | 
      cmd:                                                                                                                                                        | 
        fr: "sh -c 'set -euo pipefail; curl --fail -s --max-time 1 https://wttr.in/ | splitans -F ansi -W 104 || splitans -f neotex -F ansi docs/weather.neo'"    | 
    - key: "R"                                                                                                                                                    | 
      label:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "Rate sx"                                                                                                                                             | 
      title:                                                                                                                                                      | 
        fr: "Rate sx"                                                                                                                                             | 
      cmd:                                                                                                                                                        | 
        fr: "sh -c 'set -euo pipefail; curl --fail -s --max-time 1 https://eur.rate.sx/ | splitans -F ansi -W 104 || splitans -f neotex -F ansi docs/ratesx.neo'" | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
KEYS                                                                                                                                                              | 1:FC; 5:FP1, BP2
  q or ctrl+c  Quit                                                                                                                                               | 
  L            Cycle language (when langs is provided)                                                                                                            | 
  Layer keys   Switch to a layer defined in layers[].key                                                                                                          | 
  Arrows       Scroll the viewport when content overflows                                                                                                         | 
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
EXAMPLES                                                                                                                                                          | 1:FC; 9:FP1, BP2
  termfolio --config termfolio.yaml                                                                                                                               | 3:Fg; 36:FP1, BP2
                                                                                                                                                                  | 
NOTES                                                                                                                                                             | 1:FC; 6:FP1, BP2
  Commands are executed with sh -c, so any shell pipeline can be used. The config path is required and                                                            | 
  no default file is searched.                                                                                                                                    | 
